81
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:43,400
How can it be? We haven't
even started selling anything.

82
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:44,600
Everyone, come here!

83
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:47,200
They don't admit that
they're selling fake medicine.

84
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,800
It's you who sold me the medicine.

85
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,880
You're being ridiculous.

86
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:52,240
You're speaking loudly even
after taking our fake medicine.

87
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:54,000
It seems like our medicine is great.

88
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:56,200
You're being ridiculous.

89
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:57,360
I can prove that

90
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:59,040
Magistrate Zhang is recovering

91
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,080
after taking their medicine.

92
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:02,080
Their medicine is real.

93
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:05,160
Why are you framing them?

94
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,000
Isn't this Physician Li?

95
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,320
Physician Li?

96
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,240
That's him.

97
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,280
I've met him before.

98
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,160
That's him.

99
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,600
I want to buy some medicine!

100
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,880
- Me too!
- Me too!

101
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,240
- Give me one!
- Give me one!

102
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:22,480
Okay, please line up.

103
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,400
You're useless.

104
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:27,120
Don't push. We have more.

105
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,680
Send a letter to Zhao Baidou.

106
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,440
Thank you, everyone.

107
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,400
Just tell him

108
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,080
I want to meet him.

109
